  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_GM_AfterFire
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - Now you have access to all four core elements.
  - I grant you the rank of Novice. You may start using the alchemy table to fuse
    new elements.
  - "Don't get ahead of yourself \u2014 at your rank, only a handful of recipes are
    within reach. The more you advance, the more will reveal themselves."
  - Try making some mud. See if you can guess which two elements give you mud.
